<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca913d39-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2430"><num value="2430">§ 2430.</num><heading> Full faith and credit</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The full faith and credit of the United States is pledged to the payment of all guarantees issued under this section with respect to principal and interest.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca913d3a-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/451/tII/s211">Pub. L. 109–451, title II, § 211</ref>, <date date="2006-12-22">Dec. 22, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/3360">120 Stat. 3360</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
